casebody.data:
Miscellaneous Orders.

No. 202, Misc. Quicksall v. Michigan. Petitioner pro se. Stephen J. Roth, Attorney General of Michigan, Edmund E. Shepherd, Solicitor General, and Daniel J. O’Hara, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

The petition for appeal is denied. Treating the appeal papers as a petition for a writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Michigan, certiorari is granted and the case is ordered transferred to the appellate docket.
